  <!-- Section: Application Process -->
  <section id="application" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Application Process</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Dominica applications require licensed agents and follow a standard Caribbean CBI process. Processing takes 3-4 months—slower than St. Kitts but reasonable for the price point.
    </p>

    <ComparisonTable columns={timelineColumns} rows={timelineRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">Step-by-Step Process</h3>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Select Licensed Agent</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Choose from agents licensed by Dominica CBI Unit. Compare fees ($10,000-25,000) and success rates. Many offer free consultation. Verify license on official government website.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Document Preparation</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Gather required documents: passport copies, birth certificates, police clearances, bank statements, source of funds evidence, medical certificate, professional references. All require apostille/notarization.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Application Submission</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Agent submits complete package to CBI Unit. Application fee and due diligence fees paid. You receive confirmation and tracking number.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Due Diligence (6-8 weeks)</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Background checks via international agencies. Criminal record, financial history, sanctions screening, source of funds verification. Additional questions may be asked. This is the longest stage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">5</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Approval in Principle</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Conditional approval issued. You have 30-60 days to complete investment (EDF payment or real estate purchase). This confirms you passed due diligence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">6</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Investment Completion</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Wire EDF contribution to government account or complete real estate purchase. Agent provides wire instructions and confirms receipt.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">7</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Citizenship & Passport</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Citizenship certificate issued upon investment confirmation. Passport application processed (2-4 weeks). Can be shipped or collected. 10-year validity, renewable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 mt-6">
      <p class="text-blue-800">
        <strong>Processing timeline:</strong> Expect 3-4 months total. Unlike St. Kitts (45-day accelerated option), Dominica doesn't offer expedited processing. Budget 4 months to be safe. Peak application periods may extend timelines.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

