    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Healthcare in Dominica</h2>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Dominica is the "Nature Isle"—known for rainforests, hot springs, and eco-tourism, not medical infrastructure. The island (population ~75,000) has very limited healthcare. Most CBI citizens never reside there, but visitors should understand the limitations.
    </p>

