          <li>• No specialist care</li>
          <li>• Limited diagnostic equipment</li>
          <li>• No advanced surgery</li>
          <li>• No cardiac/cancer care</li>
          <li>• Hurricane-damaged infrastructure</li>
          <li>• Evacuation required for serious cases</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Medical Evacuation Destinations</h3>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
        <li>• <strong>Martinique:</strong> 40 minutes by air, French hospital standards (CHU de Martinique)</li>
        <li>• <strong>Guadeloupe:</strong> 30 minutes by air, French healthcare system</li>
