      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
      <p class="text-blue-800">
        <strong>Hurricane Maria impact:</strong> The 2017 hurricane significantly damaged Dominica's infrastructure including healthcare facilities. Recovery continues but facilities remain basic. If visiting for eco-tourism or diving, ensure robust evacuation coverage—the nearest proper hospital is in Martinique.
